<msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
  <locus from="2ra" to="16vb"/>
  <locus from="19ra" to="24va"/>
  <note>The folios of the manuscript are misplaced, being rearranged wrongly together: the text is in disorder.</note>
  <title type="complete" ref="LIT1450GadlaG"/>
  <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
  <incipit xml:lang="gez">
  <locus target="#2ra"></locus>
  በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ አሐዱ፡ አምላክ፨ ንቀድም፡ እንከ፡ በረድኤተ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፨ ንጽሕፍ፡ ዜናሁ፡ ለቅዱስ፡  ብእሴ፡ እግዚኣብሔር፡ ገብረ፡ ክርስቶስ።
  ወልደ፡ ቴዎዶስዮስ፡ ንጉሥ፡ ዘቈስጠንጥንያ፨፨
</incipit>
</msItem>
<msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
  <locus from="17ra" to="18vb"/>
  <locus from="25ra" to="25vb"/>
  <locus from="28ra" to="38va"/>
  <note>Number of Miracles 8. The folios are misplaced, the text is in disorder. The right order of the miracles is: ff. 28ra-35vb, 36ra-36vb, 17ra-18vb, 37ra-37vb, 25ra-25vb, 38ra-38va. Folios missing between f. 35 and f. 36, with consequent part of the text missing</note>
  <title type="incomplete" ref="LIT2384Taamme"/>
  <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
<incipit xml:lang="gez">
<locus target="#28ra"></locus>
በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ አሐዱ፡ አምላክ። ንቀድም፡ እንከ፡ በረዴተ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፨ ወእምዝ፡ ንጽሕፍ፡ ተአምሪሃ፡ ለእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ወላዲተ፡ አምላክ፡
</incipit>
<msItem xml:id="ms_i2.1">
  <locus from="28rb" to="30ra"></locus>
    <title type="complete"  subtype="miracle 1"></title>
    <textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
    <locus target="#28rb"></locus>
    ወሀሎ፡ እንከ፡ አሐዱ፡ ብእሲ፡ በአሐቲ፡ ሀገር፡ ባዕል፡ ፈድፋድ፡ ወይገብር፡ ተዝካራ፡ ለማርያም፡ ወይቄርብ፡ ቍርባነ፡ በበ፡ በዓላ፡ ለማርያም፡
    </incipit>
    </msItem>
    <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.2">
      <locus from="30ra" to="33va"></locus>
      <title type="complete" subtype="miracle 2"></title>
      <textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
      <incipit xml:lang="gez">
        <locus target="#30ra"></locus>
        ካልዕ፡ ተአምሪሃ፡ ለማርያም፡ ... ወሀሎ፡ አ(f. 30rb)ሐዱ፡ ብእሲ፡ በሃገረ፡ ቅምር፡ ክቡር፡ ዘመድ፡ በስምስ፡ ክርስትያናዊ፡
      </incipit>
    </msItem>
    <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.3">
      <locus from="33vb" to="35ra"></locus>
      <title type="complete" subtype="miracle 3"></title>
      <textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
      <incipit xml:lang="gez">
        <locus target="33vb"></locus>
          ሣልስ፡ ተአምሪሃ፡ ለማርያም፡ ... ወሀሎ፡ አሐዱ፡ ብእሲ፡ በውእቱ፡ ሃገር፡ ወሀለወት፡ ውስተ፡ ይእቲ፡ ሃገር፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡
        </incipit>
        </msItem>
        <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.4">
          <locus from="35ra" to="35vb"></locus>
          <title type="incomplete" subtype="miracle 4"></title>
          <textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
          <note>Folios missing after f. 35v: explicit missing.</note>
          <incipit xml:lang="gez">
            <locus target="#35ra"></locus>
            ራብዕ፡ ተአምሪሃ፡ ለማርያም፡ ... (f. 35rb) ወሀሎ፡ አሐዱ፡ መነኮስ፡ ዘይፈርሆ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ ዘይበኪ፡ መዓልተ፡ ወሌሊተ፡ ላዕለ፡ </incipit>
        </msItem>
        <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.5">
          <locus from="36ra" to="36va"></locus>
          <title type="incomplete" subtype="miracle 5"></title>
          <textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
          <note>Folios missing before f. 36r: incipit missing.</note>
          </msItem>
          <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.6">
          <locus from="36va" to="36vb"/>
          <locus from="17ra" to="18rb"/>
          <title type="complete" subtype="miracle 6"></title>
          <textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
          <incipit xml:lang="gez">
          <locus target="#36va"></locus>
          ሳድስ፡ ተአምሪሃ፡ ለማርያም፡ ... ወኮነት፡ እንከ፡ ብእሲት፡ መበለት፡ ነዳይት፡ ወባ(f. 36rb)ቲ፡ አሐደ፡ ወልደ፡ ወኮነት፡ ይእቲ፡ ብእሲት፡
          </incipit>
          </msItem>
          <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.7">
          <locus from="18rb" to="18vb"/>
          <locus from="37ra" to="37vb"/>
          <title type="complete" subtype="miracle 7"></title>
          <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
          <incipit xml:lang="gez">
          <locus target="#18rb"></locus>
          ሳብእ፡ ተአምሪሃ፡ ለማርያም፡... (f. 18va) ወኮነ፡ ብእሲ፡ ድያቆን፡ ይፈቅድ፡ ይትአመን፡ በእንተ፡ ኃጣውኢሁ፡ ወእከይ፡
          </incipit>
          </msItem>
          <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.8">
          <locus from="25ra" to="25vb"/>
          <locus from="38ra" to="38va"/>
          <title type="complete" subtype="miracle 8"></title>
          <textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
          <incipit xml:lang="gez">
          <locus target="#25ra"></locus>
          ሣምን፡ ተአምሪሃ፡ ዘእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ... ወሀሎ፡ ብእሲ፡ ውስተ፡ ሃገር፡ እምሠራዊተ፡ ንጉሥ፡ ክበር፡ በሀቤኁ። ወኮነ፡ ጽልሕወ፡
        </incipit> </msItem>
</msItem>
